-align: center;\">2017-12-17 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UJOWiZr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUJOWiZr.png&h=fd4a88d0&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gcM73jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgcM73jk.png&h=dc05bd20&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(10)勞嘉怡vs王敏奕(2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"334e0759838cf8854165b9672c4c6ce9c8f26240","tid":501293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃十六強抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強抽籤直播及結果"},{"pid":"11e4c570132112327b3ffadd926fe2f77621279c","tid":501293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass